5:
Wow! You really took a lot of
pictures, didn't you?
8:
Hehe. My finger just kept hitting the
button, I couldn't stop. There are
some pictures you took in there too,
Primula.
12:
Oh, I think I took this one! This is from
the show you two did. You were so
cute!
16:
Oh my. I'm really going wild in that
picture. Perhaps I overdid it...
21:
I'm not used to having pictures of
myself taken. Seeing these still
feels... weird.
24:
But at the same time... It's nice. And
fun!
29: Today's the last day of our vacation.
32: O-oh, I'm so sorry! I just...
36: I'm not done enjoying myself yet.
39:
I want to take more pictures with
you all! I've got this urge to have a
good time right until the very last
second!
43:
Me too! We've got a day to go, so
let's make the most out of it!
57:
*nom nom*
Mmm... Ee eally oo, oar ea!
61:
Delicious, isn't it? Juicy and soft, just
the way meat should be!
65:
Would you like some monster meat
sashimi? It's surprisingly good.
69:
I know a certain chef who would
take issue with you using the word
"surprisingly" there!
73:
Gosh, today just went by in a flash,
huh?
75:
We were so busy all day, but it was
so much fun! It was like living a
dream.
80: ...Echo. What do you plan to do now?
84:
Actually, I haven't decided yet. I
knew I had to make up my mind
while we were together, but I didn't...
89:
Um... Maybe it's not my place to ask
something like this, but...
95:
Ahh, I'm s-sorry! I really shouldn't pry
like that!
99:
Narcissa said she had no need for
memories.
102:
But... I do. They're important to me,
so I want to make more of
them—with the people I care about.
104:
I know some people prefer to be
alone, but that's not who I am.
107:
I want to laugh and smile with my
friends, visit different worlds, and
see all the wonderful people there!
110:
I also realized I can't keep relying on
you guys forever. I need to become
more independent.
113: But at the same time... I...
125:
It was obvious as hell we were
gonna do it anyway. Might as well
welcome her yourself.
131:
B-but, I can't do that! That's Stella's
thing! I'd feel bad.
134:
P-plus, if it's me and Pythica who
invite her, she might overthink things
and get all overly considerate again.
139:
What, you're too chicken to do
anything? Didn't we go over how
that kind of thinking gets you
nowhere?
146:
Y-you don't need to point that out!
We know!
150:
We want to be together with you
too, Echo. Let's go!
162:
W-wait... We're already outside?
What is this place? Are those stars?!
166:
Hahaha! Echo, you should see that
look on your face! Your jaw's about
to hit the floor!
170:
I mean, how could I not react that
way? I mean, we were at the bottom
of the sea, and there were
mermaids, but now we're here!
175:
Hehe. Sorry, I had to take a picture
there.
179:
Nooo! I'm probably making some
super goofy face...
182:
Um, say... Does this village have a
library?
185:
I was thinking of making an album...
And filling it with pictures of
everyone here. Could I do that?
194:
Leave space in it, cause we're gonna
be adding a WHOLE bunch more
photos to it! There are more worlds
to see!
198:
I can't wait to go exploring even
more worlds with you, Echo.
211:
I feel like I still have so much more to
do... So many things to learn. About
myself, the world, and all of you!
215:
Let's make all sorts of new memories
together!
